snippet: Simone Biles used superb floor and vault exercises to sweep past her American teammate Kyla Ross and take the lead in all-around qualifying at the world gymnastics championships.
abstract: American Simone Biles sweeps past teammate Kyla Ross to take lead in all-around qualifying at world gymnastics championships in Antwerp, Belgium.
lead_paragraph: Simone Biles used superb floor and vault exercises to sweep past her American teammate Kyla Ross and take the lead in all-around qualifying at the world gymnastics championships.

headline.main: American Leads in World Gymnastics All-Around
